Text: Description Rascal Flatts: Nothing Like This (2011):Rascal Flatts will be joined by special guests Justin Bieber and Natasha Bedingfield in their ABC concert special - "Rascal Flatts: Nothing Like This Presented by JCPenney" The hour long special will feature Flatts' performance at their January 20th concert in the Xcel Arena in St. Paul, Minnesota, a never-before-seen clip of the Justin Beiber/Rascal Flatts music video, "That Should Be Me," and behind-the-scenes footage of the making of the video.
